title: Watchmen.Script.Screenplay.Tse.Hayter.Hamm.2009
description:
This is a script pack I found online that has three different versions of the Watchmen inside it.  It has the Sam Hamm draft from 1989.  The draft by Alex Tse and a draft by David Hayter.  I&#039;m not sure which draft they are using because on IMDB it says written by Tse and Hayter.  

When an ex-superhero is murdered, a vigilante named Rorshach begins an investigation into the murder, which begins to lead to a much more terrifying conclusion.
